Cohen has condemned himself while condemning Donald Trump, and he’s produced documents to corroborate much of what he’s saying.
Cohen produced a “reimbursement” check today that was signed by Donald Trump Jr and Trump Organization CFO Allen Weisselberg.
Does Donald Trump Jr have an immunity deal?
Michael Cohen just opened the door for the House Oversight Committee to subpoena Weisselberg and Donald Trump Jr to publicly testify about this payoff and signed check.
Whether Donald Trump Jr ends up being convicted for criminally conspiring with Russia or not, he’ll definitely be convicted for his financial crimes.